'''Wolfgang Leitner''' (born 1953) is an Austrian [[billionaire]], and the CEO of [[Andritz AG]], an Austrian plant engineering company.<ref name="Forbes">{{cite web|title=The World's Billionaires: Wolfgang Leitner|url=https://www.forbes.com/profile/wolfgang-leitner/|website=Forbes|accessdate=6 February 2017}}</ref>
Leitner has a doctorate in Chemistry from the [[University of Graz]], Austria.<ref name="bloomberg.com"/>
Leitner is married, with two children, and lives in [[Graz]], Austria.<ref name="Forbes" />
